flowchart TD
  A([Start]) --> B[Receive auth request]
  B --> C{Endpoint type}
  C -->|register/login| D[Validate payload]
  C -->|refresh| E[Validate refresh token]
  C -->|logout| F[Validate access token + roles]

  D --> G[AuthApplicationService]
  E --> G
  F --> G

  G --> H{Credential or token valid?}
  H -->|No| X[Return 401 or 400]
  H -->|Yes| I[Create or rotate session]
  I --> J[Load player context]
  J --> K[Return success envelope]
  X --> Z([End])
  K --> Z
